OL,6,FThe drama series, which is inspired by
OL,7,Fthe real-life experiences of comedian
OL,8,Fand writer Mr Gadd, follows his
OL,9,Fcharacter Donny - played by Gadd -
OL,10,Fgetting stalked by a woman named
OL,11,FMartha Scott.
OL,13,FOn Piers Morgan Uncensored, Ms Harvey
OL,14,Frepeatedly denied stalking Mr Gadd in
OL,15,Freal life, as "a work of fiction, a
OL,16,Fwork of hyperbole".
