OL,7,Freferenced a scene in the show where
OL,8,Fcharacter Martha admits to
OL,9,Fintimidating Gadd's character and
OL,10,Freceives a nine-month prison sentence.
OL,12,F"That is completely untrue, very, very
OL,13,Fdefamatory to me, very career
OL,14,Fdamaging," she said.
OL,16,F"I wanted to rebut that completely on
OL,17,Fthis show ` I am not a stalker, I have
OL,18,Fnot been to jail, I've not got
