OL,6,FThe 58-year-old claimed she was
OL,7,Fprepared to go to a court of law to
OL,8,Fdefend herself against allegations
OL,9,Fmade in the series.
OL,11,FWhen Morgan asked if she will
OL,12,F"categorically be taking legal
OL,13,Faction", she replied: "Absolutely,
OL,14,Fagainst both him (Gadd) and Netflix."
OL,16,FMs Harvey said she had instructed
OL,17,Flawyers in part, but "we want to
OL,18,Fexplore all the options out there,
OL,19,Fthere are a number of people to sue".
